Maps a `Result<&mut T, E>` to a `Result<T, E>` by copying the contents of the
`Ok` part.

# Examples

```
let mut val = 12;
let x: Result<&mut i32, i32> = Ok(&mut val);
assert_eq!(x, Ok(&mut 12));
let copied = x.copied();
assert_eq!(copied, Ok(12));
```
